Text:
Congratulations to skJGZV6z for uploading this week's Stossel before my source could post it. I will not upload my flv copy this week, but will instead seed this copy.

I also enjoy Varney & Co, and would like to see more. I much prefer even the excerpts to "The Five."
Many thanks for your weekly effort to bring us crystal clear rips for this great show!
Thank you, very much for the uploads!!
